	\section{Discussion}
	The experiment turned out to be an advantage to a better control of the boat. The integration of the EPOSMoteIIs with the Android application really made the function of the pilot easier. The layout with a good usability showed itself as a great co-pilot.
	\label{sec:disc}
	\section{Conclusion}
	Putting the advantages of a WSN and the Android together, we came up with an integrated telemetry system that doesn't require a complex wire harness. The AI of the application also played a important role regarding safety and efficiency, as it warns the pilot if he is going against the tide or with it.
